permissions.moduleDes: Add, manage, and set permissions for admin users.
Manage listing of all properties including add, edit, verify, block, delete, view.
View and manage all room/PG booking requests.
Manage PG/room owners using the platform.
Manage users looking to book rooms/PGs.
Track and resolve tenant and partner complaints.
View platform earnings, commissions, and withdrawals.
View downloadable and graphical reports on platform activity.
Promote partner properties or run banner ads.
Handle subscription-based premium features.
Manage system-generated or manual notifications.
Platform-wide setup and configuration settings.
